# 📘 Books' Mathematical Proof Portal

Welcome to the official proof repository of  
**Seonghwan Yang (Books)**, who has proposed formal mathematical  
resolutions to two major open problems in number theory.

---

## 🔍 Published Proofs

### 1. Collatz Conjecture  
- 📄 Title: *Logarithmic Expectation Model Resolves the Collatz Conjecture*  
- 📎 [DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15660272](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15660272)  
- 📘 [Summary → collatz_summary.md](./collatz_summary.md)

### 2. Beal Conjecture  
- 📄 Title: *Prime Structure Instability Resolves the Beal Conjecture*  
- 📎 [DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.15660218](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15660218)  
- 📘 [Summary → beal_structure.md](./beal_structure.md)

